data.description: Wonderful one-story single-family home with several appealing features, including a pool sitted in a spacious 10,500 sq ft land. The "HOME"offers three bedrooms & two full bathrooms, porcelanato floors. The kitchen & bathrooms has been highly remodeled, featuring nice cabinets ,stainless steel appliances,, laundry room, nice stonez in the master bath and more... The second room & bath conveniently provides an exit to the pool area. With the ample land size, you have plenty of space to create a tikki bar, set up a billiard table or any amazing creative space to enjoy with friends and family.. The location: North Miami Beach is also advantageous, being just a 9-minute drive to Aventura Mall, 7 minutes to Walmart Supercenter, and close to finest restaurants,bars, shopping centers & highways.
